  "detailed_description": "Gelatina is hungry is a quick-paced arcade game that mixes absurd humor and a lot of chaos to create a frenzied and fun experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EAT ALL YOU CAN EAT</h2><br>Feel Gelatina’s hunger: <strong>eat all you can to grow more and more!</strong> The bigger you get, the more things you’ll be able to eat. And the more you eat… the more you’ll grow!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But beware! There will be <strong>enemies and obstacles</strong> in your way ready to stop you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And remember… don’t stay behind or it’ll be <strong>GAME OVER</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROM EARTH TO SPACE</h2><br>Make Gelatina advance through 18 diverse levels, growing and growing… until it reaches Outer Space!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gelatina is hungry has two parts: <strong>the Earth and Outer Space</strong>. Both have their own mechanics, enemies and… things to eat!<br><br>Furthermore, there are <strong>two game modes</strong> that modify the game’s difficulty. <br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Normal Mode: </strong>for players who want a more balanced experience.<br></li><li><strong>Extreme Mode:</strong> for players seeking a challenging and difficult gameplay.  </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE YOURSELF AND GET THE HIGHER SCORE!</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Get the best score with the points you earn by eating!</strong> Don’t leave any edibles behind and you’ll win the highest record: some things are more valuable than others!<br><br></li><li><strong>Be the quickest to complete levels and get the highest score!</strong> But don’t forget to be careful: avoid getting left behind or staying too small…</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Gelatina is hungry is a quick-paced arcade game that mixes absurd humor and a lot of chaos to create a frenzied and fun experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EAT ALL YOU CAN EAT</h2><br>Feel Gelatina’s hunger: <strong>eat all you can to grow more and more!</strong> The bigger you get, the more things you’ll be able to eat. And the more you eat… the more you’ll grow!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/6d67f27fd3a8860140517293f7486b84.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But beware! There will be <strong>enemies and obstacles</strong> in your way ready to stop you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/7eb2cf0f186d18a557f54f0a876ae024.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And remember… don’t stay behind or it’ll be <strong>GAME OVER</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/34f993f69efb2c83014cdf5b65330629.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROM EARTH TO SPACE</h2><br>Make Gelatina advance through 18 diverse levels, growing and growing… until it reaches Outer Space!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.poster.avif?t=1728402223\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.webm?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843980/extras/d5d14dc81900fd53e6199bff6c2d66e1.mp4?t=1728402223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gelatina is hungry has two parts: <strong>the Earth and Outer Space</strong>. Both have their own mechanics, enemies and… things to eat!<br><br>Furthermore, there are <strong>two game modes</strong> that modify the game’s difficulty. <br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Normal Mode: </strong>for players who want a more balanced experience.<br></li><li><strong>Extreme Mode:</strong> for players seeking a challenging and difficult gameplay.  </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE YOURSELF AND GET THE HIGHER SCORE!</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Get the best score with the points you earn by eating!</strong> Don’t leave any edibles behind and you’ll win the highest record: some things are more valuable than others!<br><br></li><li><strong>Be the quickest to complete levels and get the highest score!</strong> But don’t forget to be careful: avoid getting left behind or staying too small…</li></ul>",
